5. mutation rules

explicitly separate:
	•	read-only inputs
	•	mutable state
	•	produced outputs

main rule:

if something mutates
pass it explicitly

secondary rule:

if something is read-only
mark it const

this improves:
	•	review quality
	•	ai reliability
	•	testability
